<entry valign="middle" align="center"><term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00045">Eszopiclone</term><newline/>
(<term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00046">Lunesta</term>)</entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left"><emphasis effect="italics">Adults:</emphasis> 1 mg orally at bedtime to promote sleep. May increase to 3 mg if needed.<newline/>
