(<term class="no-emphasis" id="term-00048">Sonata</term>)</entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left"><emphasis effect="italics">Adults:</emphasis> 10 mg orally at bedtime. Maximum dose: 20 mg orally at bedtime.<newline/>
<emphasis effect="italics">Low-weight older adults and those with mild to moderate hepatic impairment:</emphasis> 5 mg orally at bedtime.</entry>
</row>
